FBIS4-46128 "jptot022__l94037" JPRS-TOT-94-022-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 22 May 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA REGIONAL AFFAIRS IDF Seizes `Terrorist' Leader al-Dirani; Hizballah Reaction IDF Seizes `Terrorist' Leader al-Dirani; Hizballah Reaction Fundamentalists Threaten Reprisal NC2205155494 Kafr Killa Voice of the South in Arabic 1530 GMT 22 May 94 NC2205155494 Kafr Killa Voice of the South Arabic BFN [Text] REUTER cites fundamentalist officials in Beirut as saying that members of their group are preparing to launch a spectacular operation against the Israelis to avenge the kidnapping of Mustafa al-Dirani, military official in charge of the so-called Believers Group, in al-Biqa' at dawn yesterday.
